{"tid":1525092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班屌人係順民嘅分化撚收得皮未","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:01:04.000Z","uid":39752,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eba6fd48eac27303dee44773866a549daa907912","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:36:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收嗲啦分化撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好將你嘅悲憤發洩返喺自己人身上<br />\n乜撚嘢抵做順民呀，唔識反抗呀<br />\n你哋知唔知你哋講嘅嘢同五年前啲屌鳩和理非嘅衝衝子一樣呀<br />\n嗰班心淡撚六月都衝撚晒出嚟喺度認屎認屁<br />\n幾經辛苦打咗成個月先令佢哋一係收聲一係做返實事<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋啲屌人順民嘅廢話唔係代表其他人真係唔識反抗呀<br />\n係你哋自己無堅持落去嘅意志呀<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n要醒就醒咗，未醒嘅俾你屌完條氣又唔順，咁屌嚟做乜呀<br />\n屌係唔會令人醒架，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>得你打咗飛機好撚爽架咋</strong></span><br />\n呢度係連登嚟呀，要醒醒晒架喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RAsbsz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RAsbsz.jpg&h=e71bfa48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日入機場，今晚做文宣<br />\n其他全部都係廢話</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9014c1163281be3486ac72c7f12369d5cefdc262","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189b7de6f1c78917272e650f8eb140078cd30713","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9258ea2b7802350e2318a7f1039932c19bb707b","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085e9b8c63ba148eb7a73944d61ca4dba828d28c","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf1c05566608857ee42514816c5a99fab7ef282","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eba61f29a9efdd91d739d1fd166e6662272acf","tid":1525092,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0445b8d5e89ed493c78925b57133a25f073a901","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159d9a60ebb628a4e92e2ac2a3f1a98f44ce7845","tid":1525092,"uid":280898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:44:37.000Z","msg":"唔該所有人喊完嬲完，用半個鐘認真諗下自己可以點升級<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dMHxdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dMHxdS</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好鬧，但每個話自己好撚嬲既人都要反思自己可以點升級"},{"pid":"d9221e2a2ed34917c34429d8f7cb15ea48ad5e38","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔記得講<br />\n六月出嚟認屎認屁嗰班我觀察九成最多只係瞓過街而無企過最前<br />\n即係同而家班冷氣撚屌咁上下<br />\n當年最前甚至一六年都有出嚟嗰班全部由頭到尾都做緊實事<br />\n如果你哋真係認同啲心淡撚嘅話<br />\n諗清楚你哋到底同緊啲乜嘢人一齊企喺高地上面屌人</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ee6da74193c6d05c74aa7282417f20372541cc75","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71641f65a80f42791da4b12b33d038198d0618f7","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ov22KSD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOv22KSD.jpg&h=50c44333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">諗清楚呢句嘢咩意思<br />\n唔只係叫你哋唔好行錯棋</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ea3e1eb1c4a70239e5f4c81fce420c4e5a9ae6ce","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fef5c1af95029c6f32ca9d41b12e3dc61349db9","tid":1525092,"uid":169646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:50:28.000Z","msg":"Push, 請停止分化, 停止互屌"},{"pid":"2573f2f2029b9e201617337ec88caa4ef8126a7c","tid":1525092,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:52:55.000Z","msg":"出面好多人屌消防<br />\n屌人唔夠出力<br />\n屌人有一絲快樂<br />\n<br />\n再唔停止就會步上日本社運舊路"},{"pid":"82b26429db9a4d3f5eca909061dd80790ea4b573","tid":1525092,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:53:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98be60bee91394584a2b830d7e29dc497d4a69a0","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e04e910ba66d7d509752cb7cacf9fcfb3a6a26d","tid":1525092,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.g